Clawitzer theme
==============

Wallpaper: wallpaper.svg (teal → navy gradient with soft waves).
Use as default in Cinnamon: System Settings → Backgrounds, or set via
/etc/dconf/db/local.d/ or the live system's default config.

Colors (clawitzer-colors.css): teal #0d9488, navy #0c4a6e.
theme/clawitzer-theme/cinnamon/ – optional Cinnamon accent overrides.
